  (text "AI COMPUTE UNIT - CORE (NCE + 4x HBM4 stacks, co-packaged)\nNCE BGA: 2500 pins, 0.8mm pitch (composite module: NCE die + silicon interposer + 4x HBM4 12-Hi)\nTFLN Photonic Engine Interface: 8ch RF differential\nHBM4 Memory: 4 stacks × 1024 lanes @ 8 Gbps/pin (interposer-internal)\nPCIe Gen 6.0 x16: 64 GT/s per lane\nV_core: 0.8V, 1000A+ (24-phase DrMOS, NCE + HBM4 combined load)" (at 152.4 30.48 0) (effects (font (size 2.0 2.0)) (justify left)))

